---
<section class="relative px-6 py-16 md:py-24 bg-[#041632] text-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="max-w-md">
      <p class="font-label text-[#ffdea5] uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-bold mb-3">Since 1971</p>
      <h1 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6 leading-tight italic">
        Global Mastery in Textile Logistics
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[#8393b5] text-lg mb-8 font-body leading-relaxed">
        Connecting Ahmedabad's heritage to the world. We ensure your textiles arrive with the same precision they were woven with.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 bg-[#1b2b48]">
          <span class="text-[#ffdea5] text-2xl font-bold block">50+</span>
          <span class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase text-[#8393b5]">Countries Served</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-[#1b2b48]">
          <span class="text-[#ffdea5] text-2xl font-bold block">4</span>
          <span class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase text-[#8393b5]">Office Locations</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="absolute -right-20 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 opacity-10 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="w-96 h-96 bg-[#775a19] blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>
</section>
